Description:
   Shard Ward is a Cleric mid-level offensive area spell. The Cleric calls
   down a barrage of razor-edged divine shards onto all enemies in the room.
   The shards are manifestations of divine judgment rendered as cutting force,
   dealing holy-physical damage to every hostile target present.

   Shard Ward is one of the Cleric's primary area-effect damage spells before
   they reach the level required for Disk's Word and Jackal's Verdict. It
   provides reliable multi-target damage in group encounters where the Cleric
   needs to contribute offensively while maintaining their support role.
   The shards have a secondary chance to reduce the target's armor class
   as they embed themselves and restrict movement.
